ttp://blavatar.com\" target=\"_blank\">Blavatars</a> (&#8220;Blog Avatars&#8221;).</li>\n<li>Added preview for drafts, scheduled and private posts.</li>\n<li>Introduced the home screen icon for comment notifications.</li>\n<li>Added a visual indicator thatÂ <a href=\"http://blackberry.trac.wordpress.org/ticket/128\">shows the post status in the post list screen</a>.</li>\n<li>Added support for Discussion settings (enable/disable comments, pingbacks and Trackbacks).</li>\n<li>Categories are now alphabetically sorted.</li>\n<li>Added the possibility to<a href=\"http://blackberry.trac.wordpress.org/ticket/17\">Â specify a resize dimension on each image</a>.</li>\n<li>Changed the image resize feature, by adding predefined dimensions loaded from the Blog Media Settings.</li>\n<li>Fixed issues on the Permissions settings screen, it now appears once at first startup.</li>\n<li>Small UI redesign.</li>\n</ul>\n<div><a href=\"http://blackberry.wordpress.org/2011/05/03/version-1-5-now-available/#gallery-1-slideshow\">Click to view slideshow.</a></div>\n<div>\n<p>Do you have questions or feedback on how we can make the app better? Please visit theÂ <a href=\"http://blackberry.forums.wordpress.org/\">WordPress for BlackBerry forums</a>Â and tell us your thoughts!</p>\n</div>\n<div>\n<p>Follow us on Twitter for the latest news:Â <a href=\"http://twitter.com/WPBlackBerry\" target=\"_blank\">@WPBlackBerry</a>.</p>\n</div>\n<br />  <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gocomments/wpblackberry.wordpress.com/464/\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/comments/wpblackberry.wordpress.com/464/\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/godelicious/wpblackberry.wordpress.com/464/\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/delicious/wpblackberry.wordpress.com/464/\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gofacebook/wpblackberry.wordpress.com/464/\"><img alt=\"\" border=\